records.addlTxt:
Sentencing proceeded.  Statements by the State, defense and defendant.  Defendant sentenced to serve 90 DAYS in the House of Correction with credit for 2 days time served; Huber privileges for work.  Court STAYED the sentence and placed defendant on Probation with the State of Wisconsin, Department of Corrections for a period of 1 YEAR.
Conditions:  
*  Possess no firearms;
*  Submit a DNA sample and pay the DNA surcharge;
*  Pay all costs and surcharges or, if not paid, convert to a civil judgment; cash bail on deposit to be applied.

Court ordered the weapon used in this matter forfeited.
